cs.RO, cs.CY, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.DC

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the use of drone fleets for automation and engineering tasks. 
- cs.CY (Computational Geometry) is also likely as the paper mentions the spatial dimensions of the structures being worked on. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the organization and coordination of the drone team. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the design and engineering of a digital platform for the drone team. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also relevant as the paper discusses the use of a digital platform to coordinate a large number of drones.
